…As Guinea Bissau visits NCC on benchmarking tour.  L-R: Mr. Ibrahim Galadima, Head, International Affairs, Nigerian Communications Commission (NCC); Mr. Teofilo Lopes, Head of Delegation from Guinea-Bissau; Prof. Umar Garba Danbatta, Executive Vice Chairman/Chief Executive Officer, NCC;  Dr. Ikechukwu Adinde, Director, Public Affairs, NCC during a benchmarking courtesy visit  to the Commission in Abuja recently.